research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Bastrop operates under a Council-Manager form of government. All council members, including the Mayor, are elected at-large. There was conflicting information regarding the current mayor, with some sources from 2023 and April 2024 mentioning Lyle Nelson, while the City of Bastrop's official website snippets and the TML City Officials Directory list Ishmael Harris as the Mayor. The information from the official city website and TML directory was prioritized for the current officials.
